503
00:38:19,120 --> 00:38:20,760
(Qiu)
Sekarang kau pasti sangat puas, 'kan?

504
00:38:21,200 --> 00:38:22,480
Baginda termakan siasatmu,

505
00:38:22,840 --> 00:38:23,720
tidak ingin mengakuiku,

506
00:38:24,280 --> 00:38:25,600
dan aku tidak punya pilihan,

507
00:38:26,000 --> 00:38:27,200
selain mengikutimu.

508
00:38:36,440 --> 00:38:37,280
Selamat untukmu,

509
00:38:38,080 --> 00:38:39,720
