572
00:43:53,840 --> 00:43:54,560
Katakanlah.

573
00:43:59,280 --> 00:44:00,840
Kenapa kau begitu baik padaku?

574
00:44:18,880 --> 00:44:19,880
Cheng Xi menghilang.

575
